WorkItem.Description:
1) Open Rawr (I was using 2.2.27).
2) Load a Mage character.
3) Go to the Options tab then Tools tab and click Cycle Analyzer button.
4) Click Optimal button which will start the process.
5) Once process is started click the X button in the top right corner of the window to close it.
6) "Object reference not set to an instance of an object" exception occurs.
